Sounds like the blue wire from the voltage regulator:

http://www.ratwell.com/technical/EngineRemoval2/12- 
VoltageRegulatorCarb.jpg

If so, there is supposed to be a tee which connects it with the blue  
wire that goes through one of the wiring grommets and up to the  
alternator light on the dash.

